name: Weng Santos
text: Also, I'm still your human cousin.  At least I think I am LOL.    It just so happens that I am also a lawyer, but a lawyer who will fight for you legally, tooth and nail in any legal proceeding, for free, no matter how big the opponent, because that's what human cousins do  =)
